After trial, the court held that the defendant Li Huiwang used fake base stations to send a total of 62,228 fraudulent text messages to an unspecified number of people, and his behavior constituted the crime of fraud.
Regarding the defender&#39;s suggestion that the defendant was an attempted offender when he was arrested, had no consequences, and had a good attitude of pleading guilty, it is recommended that the defendant be given a lighter punishment.
