The head of the Industrial Coordination Department of the National Development and Reform Commission pointed out here today that excess steel production capacity is a global problem.
In recent years, my country&#39;s capacity utilization rate has been higher than the global average, and also higher than that of the United States and Europe and other countries and regions.
Our country has taken resolute and effective measures to resolve excess production capacity, and the results are gradually showing.
The person in charge pointed out that the Party Central Committee and the State Council attach great importance to the global problem of excess steel production capacity.
